metadata.name: CONTENDERS
metadata.description:
Welcome to the 'CONTENDERS ARENA,' a collection of daring designs and vibrant styles, that celebrate the bold spirit of the LGBTQ+ community. 

Each ensemble in this collection symbolizes a unique contender, asserting their individuality with unabashed pride and charisma. Unleash your inner champion with our unique designs - they're waiting for you at Paladari. Don't hesitate, jump into the arena.
